===Verb===
'''[[houden]] [[van]]'''
# To [[love]].
#: ''Hij houdt van Belgisch bier en frieten.'' &mdash; He loves Belgian beer and French fries.
#: ''Ik hou van jou, Ienje.'' &mdash; I love you, Ienje. (A response is ''"Ik ook van jou"'' &mdash; "I love you too".)
# To [[like]].
#: ''Ik hou niet van moderne kunst.'' &mdash; I don't like modern art.
